POST http://localhost:5000/api/providers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "skill": "Electrician",
  "skills": ["wiring", "lighting"],
  "location": "Kiambu",
  "phoneNumber": "+254712345678",
  "bio": "Certified electrical technician."
}
### Get All Providers
GET http://localhost:5000/api/providers

### Filter Providers by Skill and Location
GET http://localhost:5000/api/providers?skill=Electrician&location=Kiambu

### Update an Existing Provider
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/providers/6a500d4bc0cca87f728c29ba
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "skill": "Master Electrician",
  "bio": "Certified industrial and residential electrical engineer with over 5 years experience."
}

### Delete a Provider Profile
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/providers/6a500d4bc0cca87f728c29ba